{"tid":1519663,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"所有oulipace同我入黎","createTime":"2019-08-30T15:31:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T13:26:16.000Z","uid":313904,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6fef1502ee946e91e9a9bf71e6f542be214e87f3","tid":1519663,"uid":313904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:31:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Ou Lipace係有罷課架！<br />\nOu Lipace係有罷課架！<br />\nOu Lipace係有罷課架！</span></span><br />\nLipace學生同我入曬黎一齊入tg grp傾下！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/DeAsVhbNRdz-L5Op9x5R5Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FDeAsVhbNRdz-L5Op9x5R5Q&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0vUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=7dfd7c7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/DeAsVhbNRdz-L5Op9x5R5Q</a><br />\n<br />\n下面係我地寫比校長嘅公開信：<br />\n<br />\n香港公開大學李嘉誠專業進修學院全體師生台鑒:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n有見於反對修訂逃犯條例運動進行至今已舉辦過多次遊行及集會，於六月十二日及八月十八日更有分別約二百萬人及一百七十萬人。同時運動中亦有七百多人被捕，多人受傷，一位少女因布袋彈導致失明，以及先後有八位烈士以死相諫。可惜，政府仍然漠視民意，拒絕回應市民的五大訴求。身為熱愛香港的學生，實在無法視而不見，置身事外。故此特意致函，成立罷課關注組，並且付諸實行，期望以罷課的方式響應運動，令學生的意念可以感召政府及社會各界人士，以回應社會強烈訴求。<br />\r\n有鑒於家長或各位師生會擔心學生在校外參與社會行動的安全，而學校是最安全及 能保護學生的場所，因此希望校方可以尊重同學的表達權利，並在校本的自主空間之中，與同學協調在「罷課不罷學」的前提下關注社會動盪。我們願意與校方討論各方面安排，令同學可以安全及正面思考社會問題，以實踐自主學習及回饋社會。懇請校方能夠作出妥善安排，令罷課同學能夠透過是次參與而獲得社會關注。請予批准，敬候示覆。<br />\r\n敬祝 台安<br />\r\n<br />\r\n香港公開大學李嘉誠專業進修學院罷課關注組啓<br />\n<br />\n2019年8月30日<br />\n<br />\n第一次開po，有咩錯屌得細力d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66ec4ba6c751b229facf3d4319383e41688df547","tid":1519663,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:31:19.000Z","msg":"大家唔係約定好 贏嘅時候 要除低口罩煲底相見咩<br />\n仲未到嗰個時候呀 仲未係最後呀<br />\n一齊堅持到贏唯止<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">約定大家 光復到香港嗰一刻 煲底見</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n[小心風向]最後一戰？？？？？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1519458\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1519458</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"137360b4cb29c87d9a2ea65793329fdc9657216b","tid":1519663,"uid":210059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:32:05.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c4069b22c567b7704d59f070b1698236b7e7bb8","tid":1519663,"uid":289751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:32:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1518918/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1518918/page/1</a><br />\n為了防止狗賊唔比搵律師，請各位義士發夢之前搵一個信得過既家人或者朋友交低一個時間，例如我今日去夢遊, 若果我在夜晚2200之前無報平安, 就等於出左事, 要搵律師。地點可能有少少麻煩, 要走幾轉先知, 但係都好過比人拉48個鐘。當然佢要知道你既身份證號碼同中英文全名。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.redd.it/5nobb2zmllj31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.redd.it%2F5nobb2zmllj31.jpg&h=7e932cb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.redd.it/xz7tbmcbmkj31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.redd.it%2Fxz7tbmcbmkj31.jpg&h=a1346e12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.redd.it/hb6qnadvjkj31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.redd.it%2Fhb6qnadvjkj31.jpg&h=d5f45a58&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bc2a6c64d9ab875098956d0ba0d17c126d1215da","tid":1519663,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:35:34.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831宗教集會<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />